sequenceDiagram
    User ->>+ Webapp: click login link
    Webapp -->>- User: redirect to login view
    User ->>+ Webapp: complete form and click
    Webapp ->> Gateway Service: axios.post('/login')
    Gateway Service ->> Users: axios.post('/login')

    Users ->> MariaDB: router.post(/login)
    MariaDB -->> Users: 

    Users -->> Gateway Service: 
    Gateway Service -->> Webapp: 
    Webapp -->>- User: show login confirm